## Reglas de Entrada (Input) — Zona LAN

### DNS — CT 103 (192.168.1.12)

```
config rule
    option name    'Allow-DNS-UDP'
    option src     lan
    option dest_ip 192.168.1.12
    option proto   udp
    option dest_port 53
    option target  ACCEPT

config rule
    option name    'Allow-DNS-TCP'
    option src     lan
    option dest_ip 192.168.1.12
    option proto   tcp
    option dest_port 53
    option target  ACCEPT
```

### SOAR Web — CT 104 (192.168.1.13)

```
config rule
