## Reglas de Denegación Explícita (Hardening)

```
# Bloquear acceso externo a MySQL desde WAN
config rule
    option name    'Block-MySQL-WAN'
    option src     wan
    option dest_ip 192.168.1.13
    option proto   tcp
    option dest_port 3306
    option target  REJECT

# Bloquear acceso directo desde WAN a Prometheus
config rule
    option name    'Block-Prometheus-WAN'
    option src     wan
    option dest_ip 192.168.1.11
    option proto   tcp
    option dest_port 9090
    option target  REJECT

# Regla de denegación final (drop all WAN→LAN)
config rule
    option name    'Drop-WAN-to-LAN'
    option src     wan
    option dest    lan
    option target  DROP
```

